data.description:
Nestled in the heart of Maine's stunning natural beauty, this captivating 5-bedroom (3 upstairs, 2 downstairs), 2-bathroom home is a true gem. Situated on 2.4 acres of pristine land, this property offers an idyllic retreat for those seeking a tranquil escape, just 15 minutes from Brunswick and 40 minutes from the vibrant city of Portland.

One of the most enchanting features of this property is the land that stretches behind the home. Step out of your back door and embark on a mesmerizing trail walk through the lush woods, leading you to a serene cove. This is not just a home; it's an invitation to explore the natural wonders of Maine at your doorstep.

Step inside, and you'll be welcomed by a blend of classic charm and modern amenities. This home was completely remodeled in 2022 and comes with a brand-new hot water heating system that keeps you warm and cozy throughout the year, with recently upgraded plumbing in the basement. Access to high speed, fiber optics internet services, and a ton of potential to continue upgrades in the walk-out basement. The thoughtful updates seamlessly merge with the timeless character of the home.

Georgetown, Maine, is a paradise for outdoor enthusiasts. With an abundance of trails and access to the breathtaking ocean at Reid State Park, you'll have endless opportunities for hiking, swimming, and exploring the rugged coastline. Embrace the Maine lifestyle at its finest.

This home is being sold "as is," ready to welcome its new owners with open arms. The serene surroundings and close-knit community make it the perfect place to settle down or enjoy as a vacation retreat.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of Maine's natural beauty and immerse yourself in the welcoming community of Georgetown. Act now, as this property is priced to sell quickly! Your dream home awaits.
